                                Any assignment to be given in class.Any overdue assignment won't be accepted.Group project 
                                





《 課程評分方式 》
                                1. Prompt and regular attendance 10%2. Active and intelligent participation in class discussion 10%3. Personal homework/個人作業 10% (每人至少上傳5支廣告影片於網路)4. Teamwork and project /分組報告(案例研討)  25%5. Personal Final project 25%6. Final examination 20%
                                





《 討論要求 》
                                Any group discussing to be given in class.
                                





《 其他要求 》
                                1. Prompt and regular attendance2. Active and intelligent participation in class discussion3. Teamwork of the assigned homework4. Mid-term examination5. Final examination
                                











